|dark rising||{{IPA|˧˥}}||2
|-
|voiced
|light rising||{{IPA|˩˧}}||5
|-
|rowspan=2|Departing||voiceless
|dark departing||{{IPA|˧}}||3
|-
|voiced
|light departing||{{IPA|˨}}||6
|-
|rowspan=3|Entering||rowspan=2|voiceless
|Short||upper dark entering||{{IPA|˥}}||7 (1)
